posts.post_title: Revised 9/13 Nice group of PSA Graded (or reviewed) T206 Cards
posts.post_content:
Here is the last of the T206 cards I will be selling.  Please add $5 shipping to all orders for priority mail.

Enlarged scans provided on all cards to best show condition of the cards for sale.

Please PM to reserve. 

Piedmont 350 - Frank Chance Portrait - yellow background PSA - Altered. - $95 - I think the scan will show it appears the borders were maybe "cleaned" not sure but overall a very attractive card.
